---
// Social Proof / Testimonials — 3 cards
---

<section
  id="testimonios"
  class="min-h-[calc(100vh-56px)] py-12 flex flex-col justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-surface via-deep-navy to-surface text-on-surface px-5 md:px-16 border-b border-ice-cyan/10 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, #C77B3F 0%, transparent 50%);"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-center mb-6 text-frost-white">
      Lo que dicen nuestros clientes
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-5 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-3xl mb-3">format_quote</span>
          <p class="font-body-md text-pale-blue leading-relaxed mb-4">
            "Las pizzas de masa madre son increíbles. Nuestros clientes siempre preguntan por el secreto. La calidad ultracongelada nos permite tener stock sin perder sabor."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-ice-cyan/10 pt-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-warm-copper/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper">restaurant</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-frost-white font-semibold">Restaurante Donde Pedro</p>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-pale-blue text-sm">Talca, Región del Maule</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-5 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-3xl mb-3">format_quote</span>
          <p class="font-body-md text-pale-blue leading-relaxed mb-4">
            "Las burgers premium son bestiales. Jugosas, con sabor a carne real y sin tener que descongelar. Mis clientes las aman y yo ahorro tiempo en cocina."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-ice-cyan/10 pt-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-warm-copper/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper">storefront</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-frost-white font-semibold">Carnicería La Esquina</p>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-pale-blue text-sm">Curicó, Región del Maule</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-5 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-3xl mb-3">format_quote</span>
          <p class="font-body-md text-pale-blue leading-relaxed mb-4">
            "Los cinnamon rolls son perfectos para el desayuno. Directamente del freezer al horno y quedan esponjosos. Laclientela los compra para llevar."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-ice-cyan/10 pt-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-warm-copper/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper">bakery_dining</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-frost-white font-semibold">Café Pastelería Dulce Hogar</p>
            <p class="font-body-sm text-pale-blue text-sm">Linares, Región del Maule</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
